== 2014年南非峰會 ==
第14届诺贝尔和平奖得主世界峰会原计划于2014年10月在[[南非|南非]][[开普敦|开普敦]]举行，但受到南非拒发签证给[[第十四世达赖喇嘛|第十四世达赖喇嘛]]影响，多名诺贝尔和平奖得主宣布抵制这次会议。同年10月，[[乔迪·威廉斯|乔迪·威廉斯]]宣布此次会议被取消<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/SA-Nobel-Peace-summit-cancelled-reports-20141001|title = SA Nobel Peace summit cancelled - reports|date = 2014-10-01|accessdate = 2014-10-01|website = News24|publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2014-10-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141004022234/http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/SA-Nobel-Peace-summit-cancelled-reports-20141001|dead-url = yes}}</ref>；12月，会议改在罗马召开。在12月14日的闭幕式上，[[亚特兰大市|亚特兰大市]]市长卡卡西姆·里德宣布，第15届诺贝尔和平奖得主世界峰会将在美国亚特兰大市举办<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.nobelforpeace-summits.org/mayor-reed-announces-xv-world-summit-of-nobel-peace-laureates-to-take-place-in-atlanta/|title = Mayor Reed announces XV World Summit of Nobel Peace Laureates to take place in Atlanta|date = 2014-12-15|website = World Summit of Nobel Peace Laureates|publisher = |last = |first = |deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://archive.is/20141215173027/http://www.nobelforpeace-summits.org/mayor-reed-announces-xv-world-summit-of-nobel-peace-laureates-to-take-place-in-atlanta/|archivedate = 2014-12-15|access-date = 2014-12-16}}</ref>。

